{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/energysavedetectionrate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/energysavedetectionrate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"dynamic"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Su","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/energySaveDetectionRate"},"abstract":[{"text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Defaults to 1, meaning that 1 frame per second is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 29 frames will be skipped, 1 frame is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note: Usually you set a much lower value here as for the detectionRate property to save energy.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"energySaveDetectionRate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Su","text":"UInt","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)energySaveDetectionRate","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"energySaveDetectionRate","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"energySaveDetectionRate","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}]},"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/energySaveDetectionRate":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/energySaveDetectionRate","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/energysavedetectionrate","role":"symbol","title":"energySaveDetectionRate","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su","text":"UInt"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Defaults to 1, meaning that 1 frame per second is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 29 frames will be skipped, 1 frame is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note: Usually you set a much lower value here as for the detectionRate property to save energy.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Version: 8.0.2","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","title":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","role":"collection"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","type":"topic","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","value":"occ","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading","value":"Instance Property","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/title","value":"energySaveDetectionRate","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind","value":"property","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/fragments","value":[{"text":"energySaveDetectionRate","kind":"identifier"}],"op":"replace"},{"path":"\/topicSections","value":null,"op":"add"},{"path":"\/relationshipsSections","value":null,"op":"add"},{"path":"\/seeAlsoSections","value":null,"op":"add"},{"path":"\/primaryContentSections\/0","value":{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSUInteger","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSU